Gender bias on Wikipedia refers to criticism of the online encyclopedia Wikipedia, and especially its English-language site, arguing that the nature and quantity of its content are biased due to the fact that
a dominant majority of Wikipedia editors are male.
It is among the most frequent criticisms of Wikipedia, and part of a more general criticism about systemic bias in Wikipedia…
